You are here: Einstein for Feedback Management
Check out AI-generated response summaries, survey insights dashboard, and more.

Get Insightful Perspectives from Summaries of Survey Responses
Unlock a comprehensive understanding of your survey data as generative AI summarizes responses, providing nuanced insights. Use data maps to create or update records with these summaries.
Get Deeper Insights from Survey Responses
Get the Natural Language Processing Insights dashboard for a detailed analysis of survey results based on sentiments, extracted entities, and keyphrases.
title: Einstein for Feedback Management: Unlocking Survey Insights
